author: Satoko Yasuda
title: 「あれは一体何？」猫を不思議なリュックに入れて歩く男性、街で目撃される（動画）
text: Cat Sleeping In Round Basket Two house cat sleeping in large circular cardboard tubes A sleeping tabby cat curled up in a circle. Male red cat on a couch, sleeping and forming a circular shape Cat in a box Bengal cat sleeping on yellow blanket making perfect circle. Overhead view of white cat sleeping in circular container Sleeping cat White and beige cat curled up in circular container KRAKOW, POLAND - MAY 04 :A cat sleeps at the Cat Caffee, Krowoderska 48, Krakow, Poland on May 4, 2016. The Cat Coffee is an attraction for the cat lovers and it is open since the end of June 2015 and has six cats. Two of the cats came from the ' Kocia Academia' fondation and the other four cats were or found on the street. (Photo by Omar Marques/Anadolu Agency/Getty Images)  シェア
